      <scopecontent id="aspace_5bb8768b1ee234f70095a67716ba61e4">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>Correspondence and papers relating to the <emph render="italic">Courier de Boston</emph>, a newspaper published in the 1780s, and its editor Paul Joseph Guérard de Nancrède.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
